24:45.000Z","msg":"搶向右仲扭向右<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一時間扭左 擺返直架車<br />\n同時唔好死踩迫力，1212"},{"pid":"a793fa16f01013bcbd185a2cbd5f88997aa98f8c","tid":513831,"uid":67792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:30:54.000Z","msg":"其實new york 市內應該搭地鐵會好D<br />\n渣車要搵位同埋貴無咩so"},{"pid":"b7cd98c5282b873495bb04b9da6269d6d6801fda","tid":513831,"uid":31652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:33:30.000Z","msg":"如果去New York city 最好唔揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87ac980cfdb4626d1b8cf634edfe5a83c2ae916","tid":513831,"uid":7674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"呔盤要定<br />\n唔好突然加速<br />\n均速轉灣<br />\n燈位前好多開始brake（好多十字路口都結冰）<br />\n小路出大路夠闊既話地板油可飄移"},{"pid":"b1303bcc1f5ff34f751f0abcc391b5d7a061f43f","tid":513831,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"鐵鏈"},{"pid":"78ba8c9a3e9be08806ce62e93420e6cf3c504373","tid":513831,"uid":67792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"如果任性揸，市內就渣慢D，跟住前人軑痕行，盡量個彎唔好攞咁盡。市外新手盡量唔好行country road或者state highway，行番大highway 或者toll road，佢地鏟雪會密D，出ramp唔好太快，又唔好太快落brake，預多double braking distance"},{"pid":"5f5eb17989c78f0c13a923d4f89929e5187b1f48","tid":513831,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://patch.com/new-york/new-york-city/nyc-weather-forecast-snow-extreme-cold-new-years-weekend\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpatch.com%2Fnew-york%2Fnew-york-city%2Fnyc-weather-forecast-snow-extreme-cold-new-years-weekend&d=HTkgQh88nNAuM2dD5rtKti7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d2cef705\" target=\"_blank\">https://patch.com/new-york/new-york-city/nyc-weather-forecast-snow-extreme-cold-new-years-weekend</a><br />\n<br />\n你真係唔好渣啦<br />\n唔係真係開追悼會"},{"pid":"fa9884d9a23ef6200914c386